       the individual components.
       e.g. 
    <color max="100"><red>35</red><green>50</green><blue>25</blue></color>
    <color max="65535"><red>0</red><green>0</green><blue>65535</blue></color>
    <color max="1"><red>0</red><green>0</green><blue>1</blue></color>
  -->
